    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/981b178e5b0cb2480a8f9e3cc9d156a2.webp?t=1764329921\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wonderful Handhelds</strong> is a game that allows you to collect and play fictional retro LCD games, inspired by classic devices from the 80s and 90s.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/a70f108971f648ee5233f8828d09d8a8.poster.avif?t=1764329921\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/a70f108971f648ee5233f8828d09d8a8.webm?t=1764329921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/a70f108971f648ee5233f8828d09d8a8.mp4?t=1764329921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/1aea9e265f9e22507316f61a76b28fdf.webp?t=1764329921\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi! I'm a dad making games under the name of <strong>Dad's Indie Studio</strong>. I'm also an avid collector of retro devices, especially Game&amp;Watch and Tiger Electronics, along with other lesser-known brands and models. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is a way to share my passion for collecting and playing video games in their simplest and purest form.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/f8cbb0f5fd7802b4e802c192c936c9d8.avif?t=1764329921\" width=600 height=552 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/7f2e622e945036352a1de39e661d45c2.webp?t=1764329921\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this early access release, you'll explore <strong>Cursed Castle</strong>, the first of three planned handheld games. This game pays homage to classic dungeon adventures with spooky skeletons, locked doors, and hidden keys.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/5459c56cce4399c467691389f9652160.poster.avif?t=1764329921\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/5459c56cce4399c467691389f9652160.webm?t=1764329921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/5459c56cce4399c467691389f9652160.mp4?t=1764329921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/b90568f89e0d720672e8040593f6d769.poster.avif?t=1764329921\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/b90568f89e0d720672e8040593f6d769.webm?t=1764329921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/b90568f89e0d720672e8040593f6d769.mp4?t=1764329921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/5383196b0c9683bdf0d2387f5ce9211b.poster.avif?t=1764329921\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/5383196b0c9683bdf0d2387f5ce9211b.webm?t=1764329921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/5383196b0c9683bdf0d2387f5ce9211b.mp4?t=1764329921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/f921f73b9f4c43d321330c6b18c10b20.poster.avif?t=1764329921\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/f921f73b9f4c43d321330c6b18c10b20.webm?t=1764329921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/f921f73b9f4c43d321330c6b18c10b20.mp4?t=1764329921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/dc2555c8f47a156fd380f36675d7e9dd.webp?t=1764329921\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try the demo where &quot;your friend&quot; lends you the first handheld game, Cursed Castle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play through the entire game and complete it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please note that in the full version, you’ll <strong>gain access to additional features</strong> such as score saving, the game manual, and the box, <strong>along with two more games</strong> to explore in the future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/b91711efb03564bbe6ceffd56fb8f765.webp?t=1764329921\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wonderful Handhelds is a <strong>truly indie game</strong> I’m developing in my spare time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your <strong>Wishlists</strong> and <strong>Support</strong> during early access will help fund the project and bring Wonderful Handhelds to life. Join the adventure and be part of the game's development journey!</p>",
